GENERAL PROVISIONS
NAC 483.010 Definitions.
(NRS 481.051)
1.
As used in this chapter, unless the context otherwise requires, the words and terms defined in NRS 483.030 to 483.190, inclusive, and subsections 2 and 3 of this section have the meanings ascribed to them in those sections.
2.
"Department" means the Department of Motor Vehicles.
3. "Good cause to believe" means there are facts sufficient to warrant the belief by a reasonable person that the matter in question is true.
