Persons Residing in State
NAC 483.420 "Certificate of renewal" defined.
(NRS 483.383) As used in NAC 483.420 to 483.455, inclusive, "certificate of renewal" means a certificate issued by the Department pursuant to NAC 483.445 to a person who renews his driver's license by mail.
